WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.429 --> 00:00:13.459
Payoneer is now offering a quick and
simple solution that allows you to

00:00:13.459 --> 00:00:16.309
receive credit card payments from
individuals and companies

00:00:16.309 --> 00:00:20.189
in just three simple steps. With
competitive pricing

00:00:20.189 --> 00:00:21.300
and high payment limits

00:00:21.310 --> 00:00:25.439
this is an excellent solution for
freelancers and service providers to get

00:00:25.439 --> 00:00:27.579
paid by their clients

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:30.060
To get started login to Payoneer

00:00:33.180 --> 00:00:37.110
Select Receive Payments from the
navigation menu at the top of the screen

00:00:37.110 --> 00:00:41.610
and then Request a Payment. Enter the
details of the payment you wish to

00:00:41.610 --> 00:00:42.910
receive in the form below

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:47.600
You'll begin with the payment amount and
currency

00:00:49.320 --> 00:00:50.520
the type of payment

00:00:52.830 --> 00:00:53.870
a description of the payment

00:00:55.760 --> 00:00:59.110
Please note: the maximum amount you can request per payment

00:00:59.110 --> 00:01:04.050
is $2,000. Each client can pay up to $10,000 per day

00:01:04.050 --> 00:01:08.060
so if you need to receive more than
$2,000 we suggest you do this in multiple

00:01:08.060 --> 00:01:11.090
payments. The same amounts apply in Euro too

00:01:11.090 --> 00:01:16.380
Next, fill in the information at the
individual or company you would like to

00:01:16.380 --> 00:01:17.390
receive payment from

00:01:17.390 --> 00:01:21.410
Note that we will save this information
to make it easier for you to send future

00:01:21.410 --> 00:01:24.370
payment requests

00:01:24.370 --> 00:01:27.780
To see a preview of the payment request
email you're about to send

00:01:27.780 --> 00:01:32.060
select Preview. The email will include details of your request

00:01:32.060 --> 00:01:35.810
such as amount and description and the
Pay Now button for your client to

00:01:35.810 --> 00:01:38.410
complete the payment with a Visa or
MasterCard

00:01:38.410 --> 00:01:41.590
When you're satisfied with the details
of your email

00:01:41.590 --> 00:01:46.780
Press Send. The email will inform the company or individual of  your payment request

00:01:46.780 --> 00:01:50.200
and with a couple of clicks will allow
them to easily complete the payment

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:52.170
using a Visa or MasterCard

00:01:52.170 --> 00:01:55.840
All payments are reviewed on an
individual basis and are subject to

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:57.130
approval by Payoneer

00:01:57.130 --> 00:02:01.160
Once approved, funds are available within
two business days

00:02:01.160 --> 00:02:05.930
It's a simple as 1, 2, 3! For additional
assistance

00:02:05.930 --> 00:02:09.709
or if you have any questions, please
don't hesitate to contact us

00:02:09.709 --> 00:02:13.660
by going to www.payoneer.com

00:02:13.660 --> 00:02:15.200
and clicking on Support Center

